News of htmlview

* 0.4.0 (2013-02-18)

  * fix a bug that conflicts other plugin
  * use font size setting from sylpheedrc
  * support GtkHTML

* 0.3.0 (2012-08-01)

  * depends on show_attach_tab option for rendering HTML
  * add 'Show HTML as default' option

* 0.2.1 (2012-06-30)

  * fix grab focus problem

* 0.2.0 (2012-06-28)

  * added options(enable-private-browsing,auto-load-images,enable-scripts)

* 0.1.0 (2012-06-24)

  * initial release
